.Dd June 4, 2025
.Dt LFACME 7
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm lfacme cert
.Nd manage ACME certificates
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm lfacme
.Op opts
.Cm cert list
.Nm lfacme
.Op opts
.Cm cert remove
.Ar certificate
.Op Ar certificate ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
command is used to manage certificates issued by
.Xr lfacme 8 .
.Pp
The following commands are supported:
.Bl -tag -width Cm remove
.It Cm list
List issued certificates.
.It Cm remove
Remove the given certificates.
The certificates will be deleted from the disk, but will be reissued the next
time
.Xr lfacme-renew 8
is run unless they are also removed from
.Xr domains.conf 5 .
.Sh ENVIRONMENT
Refer to
.Xr lfacme 8
for a list of environment variables which affect the operation of
.Nm .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr domains.conf 5 ,
.Xr lfacme 8
